doctype html
html
  head
    title Bull.sh - Charte graphique
    include ../commons/meta
    include ../commons/includes
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/charte-graphique/index.css')
  body
    // Page Wrapper
    .page-wrapper
      // Header
      include ../commons/header

      // Main
      article#main
        include ../commons/pages/article-header.mixin.pug
        +articleHeader('Charte graphique', 'Eléments graphiques et design')

        section.wrapper.bg-white.fg-black
          .inner
            h4 Pr&eacute;sentation
            p Cette page d&eacute;crit l'ensemble des &eacute;l&eacute;ments graphiques qui devront &ecirc;tre utilis&eacute;s sur le site de Bull.sh et sur l'application associ&eacute;e.&nbsp;
              | Chaque &eacute;l&eacute;ment &agrave; &eacute;t&eacute; pens&eacute; pour donner &agrave; Bull.sh sa propre identit&eacute; visuelle.
            p Il est &eacute;galement &agrave; que le menu de droite et le header de cette page font partie de la charte graphique.
            section
              h4 Colors
              p Comme d&eacute;fini dans&nbsp;
                a(href='#') le document associ&eacute;
                | , les couleurs qui devront &ecirc;tre utilis&eacute;e sur le site sont les suivantes:
              .row.uniform(class='50%')
                div(class='6u 12u(medium)')
                  span.image.fit
                    img(src='/assets/images/palette.png')
                div(class='6u 12u(medium)')
                  span.image.fit
                    img(src='/assets/images/palette_l-d.png')
              hr
            section
              h4 Text & headings
              p Le texte devra suivre les guidelines suivantes:
              p
                | This is&nbsp;
                b bold&nbsp;
                | and this is&nbsp;
                strong strong
                | . This is&nbsp;
                i italic&nbsp;
                | and this is&nbsp;
                em emphasized
                | .
                | This is&nbsp;
                sup superscript&nbsp;
                | text and this is&nbsp;
                sub subscript&nbsp;
                | text.
                | This is&nbsp;
                u underlined
                | &nbsp;and this is code:&nbsp;
                code for (;;) { ... }
                | . Finally,&nbsp;
                a(href='#') this is a link
                | .
              h2.fg-black Heading Level 2
              h3 Heading Level 3
              h4 Heading Level 4
              h5 Heading Level 5
              h6 Heading Level 6
              hr
              h4 Blockquote
              blockquote.fg-black
                p
                  span.quote.quote-begin “
                  | Fringilla nisl. Donec accumsan interdum nisi, quis tincidunt felis sagittis eget tempus euismod. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus vestibulum. Blandit adipiscing eu felis iaculis volutpat ac adipiscing accumsan faucibus. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus lorem ipsum dolor sit amet nullam adipiscing eu felis.
                  span.quote.quote-end ”
                cite - Someone, somewhere
              hr
            section
              h4 Lists
              .row
                div(class='6u 12u$(medium)')
                  h5 Unordered
                  ul
                    li Dolor pulvinar etiam.
                    li Sagittis adipiscing.
                    li Felis enim feugiat.
                div(class='6u$ 12u$(medium)')
                  h5 Ordered
                  ol
                    li Dolor pulvinar etiam.
                    li Etiam vel felis viverra.
                    li Felis enim feugiat.
                    li Dolor pulvinar etiam.
                    li Etiam vel felis lorem.
                    li Felis enim et feugiat.
              hr
              h4 Icons
                ul.icons
                  li
                    a.icon.fa-twitter(href='#')
                      span.label Twitter
                  li
                    a.icon.fa-facebook(href='#')
                      span.label Facebook
                  li
                    a.icon.fa-instagram(href='#')
                      span.label Instagram
                  li
                    a.icon.fa-github(href='#')
                      span.label Github
              hr
            section
              h4 Actions
              .row
                div(class='12u')
                  ul.actions
                    li
                      a.button.special(href='#') Default
                    li
                      a.button.secondary(href='#') Secondary
                  ul.actions
                    li
                      a.button.special(href='#')
                        i.icon.fa-envelope-o
                        span Default
                    li
                      a.button.secondary(href='#')
                        i.icon.fa-envelope-o
                        span Secondary
              .row.bg-primary
                div.container(class='12u')
                  ul.actions
                    li
                      a.button.special(href='#') Default
                    li
                      a.button.secondary(href='#') Secondary
                    li
                      a.button.secondary-hover(href='#') Secondary hover
                  ul.actions
                    li
                      a.button.special(href='#')
                        i.icon.fa-envelope-o
                        span Default
                    li
                      a.button.secondary(href='#')
                        i.icon.fa-envelope-o
                        span Secondary
                    li
                      a.button.secondary-hover(href='#')
                        i.icon.fa-envelope-o
                        span Secondary hover
              .row.bg-accent-base
                div.container(class='12u')
                  ul.actions
                    li
                      a.button.secondary(href='#') Secondary
                    li
                      a.button.secondary-hover(href='#') Secondary hover
                  ul.actions
                    li
                      a.button.secondary(href='#')
                        i.icon.fa-envelope-o
                        span Secondary
                    li
                      a.button.secondary-hover(href='#')
                        i.icon.fa-envelope-o
                        span Secondary hover
              hr

            section
              h4 Form
              form(method='post', action='#')
                .row.uniform
                  div(class='6u 12u$(xsmall)')
                    input#demo-name(type='text', name='demo-name', value='', placeholder='Name')
                  div(class='6u$ 12u$(xsmall)')
                    input#demo-email(type='email', name='demo-email', value='', placeholder='Email')
                  div(class='12u$')
                    .select-wrapper
                      select#demo-category(name='demo-category')
                        option(value='') - Category -
                        option(value='1') Manufacturing
                        option(value='1') Shipping
                        option(value='1') Administration
                        option(value='1') Human Resources
                  div(class='4u 12u$(small)')
                    input#demo-priority-low(type='radio', name='demo-priority', checked='')
                    label(for='demo-priority-low') Low
                  div(class='4u 12u$(small)')
                    input#demo-priority-normal(type='radio', name='demo-priority')
                    label(for='demo-priority-normal') Normal
                  div(class='4u$ 12u$(small)')
                    input#demo-priority-high(type='radio', name='demo-priority')
                    label(for='demo-priority-high') High
                  div(class='6u 12u$(small)')
                    input#demo-copy(type='checkbox', name='demo-copy')
                    label(for='demo-copy') Email me a copy
                  div(class='6u$ 12u$(small)')
                    input#demo-human(type='checkbox', name='demo-human', checked='')
                    label(for='demo-human') Not a robot
                  div(class='12u$')
                    textarea#demo-message(name='demo-message', placeholder='Enter your message', rows='6')
                  div(class='12u$')
                    ul.actions
                      li
                        input.special(type='submit', value='Send Message')
            section
              h4 Notifications
              a#notif.button.special Click me
      include ../commons/footer

    // Scripts
    script(src='/charte-graphique/index.js')
